'''希望号'''（{{lang-en|Omid}}，{{lang-fa|'''امید'''}}，意为“希望”<ref name="individual.com">{{cite web
|url=http://www.individual.com/story.php?story=77178693
|title=伊朗在空间研究中心发射希望号
|publisher=individual.com
|date=February 4, 2008
|accessdate=2008-02-04
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080507070102/http://www.individual.com/story.php?story=77178693
|archive-date=2008-05-07
|dead-url=yes
}}</ref>）是[[伊朗|伊朗]]首颗自行研制的[[人造卫星|人造卫星]]。<ref name=Reuters>{{cite news | title = 伊朗发射首颗自行研制人造卫星：国家电视台 | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idUSTRE5120NN20090203 | publisher = [[路透社|路透社]] | date = Feb 3, 2009 | accessdate = Feb 3, 2009 | author = Fredrik Dahl and Edmund Blair | archive-date = 2021-01-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126205838/https://www.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idUSTRE5120NN20090203 | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[伊朗国家电视台|伊朗国家电视台]]报道说2009年2月2日成功发射了一颗用于科研和通讯的数据处理人造卫星。<ref name=Reuters/><ref>{{cite web 
 |title=Iran puts Omid data-processing satellite into orbit 
 |publisher=[[IRNA|IRNA]] 
 |url=http://www5.irna.ir/En/View/FullStory/?NewsId=335409&IdLanguage=3 
 |date=2009-02-03 
 |accessdate=2009-02-03 
 |deadurl=yes 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090206161943/http://www5.irna.ir/En/View/FullStory/?NewsId=335409&IdLanguage=3 
 |archivedate=2009-02-06 
 }}</ref>伊朗自行研制的 “[[信使号_(火箭)|信使号 2]]”（Safir）[[运载火箭|运载火箭]]发射升空后，卫星已经被送入[[低地轨道|低地轨道]]。本次发射恰逄[[伊朗革命|伊朗革命]]的30周年庆典，[[伊朗总统|总统]][[马赫茂德·艾哈迈迪-内贾德|内贾德]]出席了发射仪式，并开启卫星传送信号“[[大赞辞|Allāhu Akbar]]”（真主至大）。<ref name=launching>{{cite web|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/video/2009/feb/03/iran-satellite-launch|title=Mahmoud Iran launches homegrown satellite|date=2009-02-03|accessdate=2009-02-04|archive-date=2013-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130211034039/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/video/2009/feb/03/iran-satellite-launch|dead-url=no}}</ref>他说发射这颗卫星是为了向全世界传播“[[一神论|一神论]]，和平和公正”。<ref name=homegrown>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/middle_east/7866357.stm|title=Iran launches homegrown satellite|date=2009-02-03|accessdate=2009-02-04|archive-date=2017-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809060826/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/middle_east/7866357.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>伊朗外交部长[[马努切赫尔·穆塔基|马努切赫尔·穆塔基]]说发射这颗卫星完全是为了“满足国家需要”，“纯粹是为了和平的目的”。<ref name=homegrown/>

希望号是伊朗的第二颗在轨卫星。2005年[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]为[[伊朗|伊朗]]制造并发射了一颗名为[[Sina-1|Sina-1]]的卫星<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/world/2008-02-17-iran-space_N.htm|publisher=今日美国|title=Iran space rocket successfully transmits data|date=2008-02-17|accessdate=2009-02-04|archive-date=2011-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928103117/http://www.usatoday.com/news/world/2008-02-17-iran-space_N.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBC4381436">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/4381436.stm|title=第一颗伊朗卫星发射成功|date=27 October 2005<!--, 09:30 GMT-->|publisher=BBC|language=en|accessdate=2008-08-17|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125013402/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/4381436.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。希望号卫星装载有卫星控制装置及动力供应系统，可用于收集情报和对设备进行检验。但很多功能还没全部激活<ref name="Robert Tait">{{cite news | author=Robert Tait | 2= | title=Iran launches first domestically produced satellite | date=3 February 2009 | publisher= | url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/feb/03/iran-satellite-launch-omid | work=guardian | pages= | accessdate=2009-02-13 | language= | archive-date=2013-07-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130702223624/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/feb/03/iran-satellite-launch-omid | dead-url=no }}</ref>。伊朗表示发射卫星是为了改进通信技术和互联网应用技术和监测自然灾害等用途，但是西方分析家则认为此举将等于为该国增加了发射[[洲际弹道导弹|洲际弹道导弹]]的能力<ref name="Robert Tait" />。

== 实验发射 ==
2008年2月4日，在新航天中心揭幕仪式上内贾德总统宣布，希望号将会在不久的将来发射升空。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.debka.com/headline.php?hid=5000 | title = DEBKAfile - 伊朗发射首枚空间研究火箭Safir 1 | access-date = 2009-02-04 | archive-date = 2009-09-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090903225225/http://www.debka.com/headline.php?hid=5000 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 轨道 ==
该卫星为了避免飞跃邻国采用的发射方向是东南方，越过[[印度洋|印度洋]]，[[轨道倾角|轨道倾角]]为55.5度。<ref>{{citation | title = Iran puts satellite into Earth orbit | author = Stephen Clark | url = http://spaceflightnow.com/news/n0902/03iran/ | magazine = Spaceflight Now | date = February 3, 2009 | accessdate = 2009-02-04 | archive-date = 2021-02-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210211211008/https://spaceflightnow.com/news/n0902/03iran/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>轨道高度据报道为246──377[[公里|公里]]， 轨道周期90.76分钟。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.heavens-above.com/orbit.aspx?satid=33506&lat=0&lng=0&loc=Unspecified&alt=0&tz=CET|title=Omid - Orbit Data|publisher=Heavens Above|accessdate=2009-02-04|archive-date=2020-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814172807/https://www.heavens-above.com/orbit.aspx?satid=33506&lat=0&lng=0&loc=Unspecified&alt=0&tz=CET|dead-url=no}}</ref>

